:0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f82612459fc30c77353839576b0b59b49fba4594","tid":942209,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:06:35.000Z","msg":"做long straddle"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:22:49.000Z","msg":"依個真係要博佢爆幾十% 先玩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dab5cc9669a9247e6f860d287b8953fd53d484f","tid":942209,"uid":121610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:04:19.000Z","msg":"屌 最大問題咪又係你點「賭」佢業績好定差<br />\n如果鳩賭，expected value 好大機會負 （錯方向、平開、vol縮）"},{"pid":"8df7fd5617b846f972c46e4f748140f7812a7957","tid":942209,"uid":93161,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T00:14:28.000Z","msg":"你個assumption（贏錢機率&gt;50%)根本就完全唔合理，有學過基本expected value都唔應該會犯既錯。 首先，你果3個situation（好過預期、平開、差過）既機率完全唔一樣，之後你用一個唔係對等既機率去乘一個唔對等既expected value，出黎既expected return根本就會錯。你既assumption可以用一個極端例子解釋：<br />\n<br />\n買六合彩會有以下兩個情況<br />\n1. 中 派800萬 <br />\n2.唔中 輸左10蚊買飛錢<br />\n<br />\n所以長買一定會贏大錢，而事實係咪咁呢？"},{"pid":"d5e4b89334e004601745da8ced4a2ed8a48801b9","tid":942209,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T01:57:42.000Z","msg":"如果你加個filter判斷到邊啲公司業績有驚喜。或者熊市long put, 牛市long call, 或者可以提高回報率"},{"pid":"0f85928747883ea47194920d5a3ef457a53bed95","tid":942209,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f82612459fc30c77353839576b0b59b49fba4594","tid":942209,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:06:35.000Z","msg":"做long straddle"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T02:05:26.000Z","msg":"一磨縮兩邊引伸就兩邊一齊GG"},{"pid":"e365db8bb2c71a77f1859252fe930b08f72836a4","tid":942209,"uid":169656,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T03:14:28.000Z","msg":"今次發達啦 一定work<br />\n原來錢真係會從天而降<br />\n<br />\n樓主要快d行動，陣間傳左開去人人都知就冇得賺喇"},{"pid":"c65dede0efa78e24c30b5575667afe695edeef77","tid":942209,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f85928747883ea47